= Rendering enhancements ====

-- Immediate: Start using the Cairo "scaled font" API: http://cairographics.org/manual/cairo-cairo-scaled-font-t.html

-- Long-term: Convert to Pango, the "real" text API in Cairo: http://library.gnome.org/devel/pango/unstable/
              ... or Convert to GD:
                  http://www.libgd.org/Basics
                  http://www.libgd.org/Reference
